; Test times.cc "in February" period expression
; via handle_in_token in parse()

2025/12/01 Dec tx
    Expenses:Food   $5.00
    Assets:Cash

2026/02/15 Feb tx
    Expenses:Food   $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2026/03/01 Mar tx
